  "commit_message": "Support DSSE bundles with Rekor v2 hashedrekord entries (#1677)\n\nsigstore-conformance v0.0.29 introduces DSSE bundles whose transparency\nlog entry is a hashedrekord/0.0.2 whose digest is computed over the DSSE\npre-authentication encoding (PAE) rather than the envelope payload.\n\nAdd a `compareSignedDigest` method to `SignatureContent` that compares\nagainst the digest of the bytes the signature actually covers (PAE for\nDSSE, message digest for message signatures) and use it when verifying\nhashedre",
